title: :: Reclassification of wet nitrousulose by the anti-terrorist agency as a high-explosion substance
subtitle: Pending industry intervention, the Government's reclassification of the anti-nitrosulose component from "non-explosive" to "high explosives" has been removed.
author: David Emery
vclaim: The Bureau of Alcohol, Firearms and Tobacco has reclassified wet nitrosulose as a high explosive.
